ibis.cashmere.constellation

Class LibFunc

  • java.lang.Object
    • ibis.cashmere.constellation.LibFunc

  • public class LibFunc
extends java.lang.Object
    A LibFunc represents an entry point to an OpenCL library. From this LibFunc we can create more than one LibFuncLaunch instances with which the library function can be launched.
